Open HouseOpen House is tonight pm starting in the cafeteria It starts with a preview of clubs then a general meeting then classroom visitations then another club preview There will be no time for individual conferencing but you will at least have the opportunity to meet your childs teachers Ill give some kind of reward to my students if their parents come havent decided what yet but theyll get something I look forward to meeting you Wendy Koebernick Wells MS English
behavior updateJust letting you know that I had to correct Candis for talking in class today on more than one occasion I did not assign her a consequence Wendy Koebernick English

open house dategradesJust a word to let you know that Open House has been rescheduled for Oct Not sure of the time yet Also this is the last week of the six weeks so the kids only have until Friday to get makeup work turned in to me If you have not signed and returned a letter stating that your child has received hisher grammar textbook please be sure you get that letter returned to me by Friday I did count it as a grade so your child will receive a zero unless I have something from you stating this I updated their grades this weekend so if you would like to know your childs current status feel free to ask Wendy Koebernick Wells M S English

detention noticeI assigned Candis detention for tomorrow afternoon She walked into class this morning and announced that she was leaving to go to the restroom without waiting for my response and then was tardy to class

progress reportsFYI Progress reports will be distributed Monday Oct Our grades are due this Thursday at pm As a result you should expect to see the kids doing lots makeup work in all classes this week I told most of the kids their current grades today and told them what zeros they have I will talk to the rest of them tomorrow I have attached an assignment sheet so that you know whats up Please feel free to respond and ask me for current grade status I will be sending home detailed reports on Friday that will require your signature Thanks Hope you all had a great weekend Wendy Koebernick Wells MS English
